"Harmonia" means the Software product released by the Licensor under this License.

"Hosted or managed service" means a service in which you or someone acting for you runs the Software for the benefit of a third party and that third party is given access to, control over, or the ability to materially use the Software itself, including its core agent features, APIs, administrative features, orchestration, configuration, tools, or extensions. A hosted or managed service does not include:

(i) consulting, customization, support, or operational assistance for a deployment that exists in the customer's own environment;

(ii) use of the Software solely as an internal tool to produce outputs or deliverables for a client, where the client is not granted general-purpose access to the Software itself; or

(iii) incidental or limited display of output generated by the Software that does not amount to the customer receiving Harmonia itself as an online service.

